detectors.description:
Reentrancy in DecentrEx.trade(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,address,uint8,bytes32,bytes32,uint256) ():
	External calls:
	- tradeBalances(tokenGet,amountGet,tokenGive,amountGive,user,amount) ()
		- accountLevel = AccountLevels(accountLevelsAddr).accountLevel(user) ()
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- orderFills[user][hash] = safeAdd(orderFills[user][hash],amount) ()
	DecentrEx.orderFills () can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- DecentrEx.amountFilled(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,address,uint8,bytes32,bytes32) ()
	- DecentrEx.availableVolume(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,address,uint8,bytes32,bytes32) ()
	- DecentrEx.cancelOrder(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,uint8,bytes32,bytes32) ()
	- DecentrEx.trade(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,address,uint8,bytes32,bytes32,uint256) ()
detectors.markdown:

		- [accountLevel = AccountLevels(accountLevelsAddr).accountLevel(user)]()
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- [orderFills[user][hash] = safeAdd(orderFills[user][hash],amount)]()
	[DecentrEx.orderFills]() can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- [DecentrEx.amountFilled(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,address,uint8,bytes32,bytes32)]()
	- [DecentrEx.availableVolume(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,address,uint8,bytes32,bytes32)]()

	- [DecentrEx.trade(address,uint256,address,uint256,uint256,uint256,address,uint8,bytes32,bytes32,uint256)]()

detectors.description:
Reentrancy in DecentrEx.tradeBalances(address,uint256,address,uint256,address,uint256) ():
	External calls:
	- accountLevel = AccountLevels(accountLevelsAddr).accountLevel(user) ()
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- tokens[tokenGet][msg.sender] = safeSub(tokens[tokenGet][msg.sender],safeAdd(amount,feeTakeXfer)) ()
	- tokens[tokenGet][user] = safeAdd(tokens[tokenGet][user],safeSub(safeAdd(amount,feeRebateXfer),feeMakeXfer)) ()
	- tokens[tokenGet][feeAccount] = safeAdd(tokens[tokenGet][feeAccount],safeSub(safeAdd(feeMakeXfer,feeTakeXfer),feeRebateXfer)) ()
	- tokens[tokenGive][user] = safeSub(tokens[tokenGive][user],safeMul(amountGive,amount) / amountGet) ()
	- tokens[tokenGive][msg.sender] = safeAdd(tokens[tokenGive][msg.sender],safeMul(amountGive,amount) / amountGet) ()
detectors.markdown:
Reentrancy in [DecentrEx.tradeBalances(address,uint256,address,uint256,address,uint256)]():
	External calls:
	- [accountLevel = AccountLevels(accountLevelsAddr).accountLevel(user)]()
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- [tokens[tokenGet][msg.sender] = safeSub(tokens[tokenGet][msg.sender],safeAdd(amount,feeTakeXfer))]()
	- [tokens[tokenGet][user] = safeAdd(tokens[tokenGet][user],safeSub(safeAdd(amount,feeRebateXfer),feeMakeXfer))]()
	- [tokens[tokenGet][feeAccount] = safeAdd(tokens[tokenGet][feeAccount],safeSub(safeAdd(feeMakeXfer,feeTakeXfer),feeRebateXfer))]()
	- [tokens[tokenGive][user] = safeSub(tokens[tokenGive][user],safeMul(amountGive,amount) / amountGet)]()
	- [tokens[tokenGive][msg.sender] = safeAdd(tokens[tokenGive][msg.sender],safeMul(amountGive,amount) / amountGet)]()
